{{DISPLAYTITLE:Dragon Warrior IV - Map List}}

This page documents all map locations in Dragon Warrior IV for the NES.

==Map System Overview==

Maps in DW4 are organized into map groups, each containing multiple submaps. Map data is stored primarily in Bank $09.

===Map ID Format===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Bits !! Description
|-
| 7-4 || Submap index within map group
|-
| 3-0 || Map group ID
|}

